Mayor & Trustees,

Due to the nature of the flyers posted around Town and on social media depi=
cting my image superimposed on the image of King Leopold II of Belgium, and=
 their placement next to the =91No Kings=92 Rally posters, I don=92t feel s=
afe being in Town this weekend with my family. We=92ve had to install more =
cameras around our house to watch doors and windows since our neighbors hav=
e acted foolishly over the last several months, and our neighbor is one of =
the people behind posting and distributing flyers across town. With 500-600=
 people in Town for political reasons, and with my image as a king being po=
sted next to flyers for the rally, I think it best that my family and I lea=
ve Town for the weekend and will return on Sunday.

If you need to reach me, my work mobile is below.

In Public Service,

[cid:image001.png@01DCBD31.6241AA30]
Stefen Wynn, M.P.A.
